(145, 'Laptop Lenovo ThinkPad T14 Gen 3 21AJS18000', 't14_1_1734659501.jpg', '21,990,000', '<ul>\n<li><strong>T&ecirc;n sản phẩm</strong>:&nbsp;Laptop Lenovo ThinkPad T14 Gen 3 (21AJS18000)</li>\n<li><strong>Bộ vi xử l&yacute;</strong>:&nbsp;Intel Core i5-1235U (Bộ nhớ đệm 12M, l&ecirc;n đến 4,40 GHz)</li>\n<li><strong>Bộ nhớ ram</strong>: 16GB DDR4 3200MHz</li>\n<li><strong>Dung lượng ổ cứng</strong>:&nbsp;256GB SSD M.2 2280 PCIe x4 NVMe</li>\n<li><strong>K&iacute;ch thước m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh</strong>: 14 inch WUXGA (1920 x 1200)</li>\n<li><strong>Card graphics:</strong>&nbsp;Intel Iris Xe Graphics</li>\n<li><strong>Ổ đĩa quang</strong>: Kh&ocirc;ng</li>\n<li><strong>Cổng</strong>:&nbsp;1x USB 3.2 Gen 1; 1x USB 3.2 Gen 1 (Always On); 2x Thunderbolt 4 / USB4 40Gbps (support data transfer, Power Delivery 3.0 and DisplayPort 1.4); 1x HDMI, up to 4K/60Hz; 1 x MicroSD card reader; 1x Headphone / microphone combo jack (3.5mm)</li>\n<li><strong>wifi kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y:</strong>&nbsp;Intel AX211 Wi-Fi 6E, 2x2; 1 x Jack LAN (100/1000M (RJ-45)); Bluetooth v5.1</li>\n<li><strong>Webcam</strong>:&nbsp;FHD 1080p</li>\n<li><strong>Loại pin</strong>:&nbsp;4Cell 52.5WHr</li>\n<li>Đen</li>\n<li>&nbsp;No OS</li>\n<li><strong>K&iacute;ch thước trọng lượng:</strong>&nbsp;317.7 x 226.9 x 17.9 mm; 1.21 kg&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>Bảo h&agrave;nh</strong>: 36Thang</li>\n</ul>', 0, 1, 0.00, 'inactive', 1000, '', '', 0, 'publish', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2024-12-20 01:53:44', '2024-12-20 01:53:58', 'laptop lenovo thinkpad t14 gen 3 21ajs18000', 'laptop lenovo thinkpad t14 gen 3 21ajs18000 21,990,000 t&ecirc;n san pham:&nbsp;laptop lenovo thinkpad t14 gen 3 (21ajs18000) bo vi xu l&yacute;:&nbsp;intel core i5-1235u (bo nho dem 12m, l&ecirc;n den 4,40 ghz) bo nho ram: 16gb ddr4 3200mhz dung luong o cung:&nbsp;256gb ssd m.2 2280 pcie x4 nvme k&iacute;ch thuoc m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh: 14 inch wuxga (1920 x 1200) card graphics:&nbsp;intel iris xe graphics o dia quang: kh&ocirc;ng cong:&nbsp;1x usb 3.2 gen 1; 1x usb 3.2 gen 1 (always on); 2x thunderbolt 4 / usb4 40gbps (support data transfer, power delivery 3.0 and displayport 1.4); 1x hdmi, up to 4k/60hz; 1 x microsd card reader; 1x headphone / microphone combo jack (3.5mm) wifi kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y:&nbsp;intel ax211 wi-fi 6e, 2x2; 1 x jack lan (100/1000m (rj-45)); bluetooth v5.1 webcam:&nbsp;fhd 1080p loai pin:&nbsp;4cell 52.5whr den &nbsp;no os k&iacute;ch thuoc trong luong:&nbsp;317.7 x 226.9 x 17.9 mm; 1.21 kg&nbsp; bao h&agrave;nh: 36thang '),
